78098", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8d2e/f026/62072_large.png?m=1401978098", "created": 1399393728, "last_modified": 1401978098}, "last_reply_by": "whooami", "last_touched": 1686104325, "title": "15 寸 MacBook air 真是个超级大败笔， 12 寸 MacBook 才是刚需啊！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/946284", "created": 1686032260, "deleted": 0, "content": "12 寸 MacBook 的外形，键盘换成新的 1mm 剪刀脚，芯片换成 m2 。\r\n900g 的机身，不比这 15 寸 air 好到天上去！？\r\n那么大那么重的 air 还是 air 吗？哎", "content_rendered": "<p>12 寸 MacBook 的外形，键盘换成新的 1mm 剪刀脚，芯片换成 m2 。\n900g 的机身，不比这 15 寸 air 好到天上去！？\n那么大那么重的 air 还是 air 吗？哎</p>\n", "last_modified": 1686032260, "replies": 82, "id": 946284}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 4439, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1138, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 74159, "username": "mie", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/mie", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9924/3aab/74159_mini.png?m=1422427664", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9924/3aab/74159_normal.png?m=1422427664", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9924/3aab/74159_large.png?m=1422427664", "created": 1410923878, "last_modified": 1422427664}, "last_reply_by": "hjw45611", "last_touched": 1686005573, "title": "生娃还是需要冷静点想一想", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/946334", "created": 1686039469, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近亲戚一对小年轻有了娃，虽然是一件喜事，但是后来两人冷静下来一想，还是觉得有点能力不足，生不起。。。。\r\n\r\n位置：广东 18 线城市\r\n男方：月入 5000 ，无社保，每月 3000 车贷 \r\n（车贷我觉得是过高了，但是结婚这种事，算你情我愿吧。房子目前买不起，但是也要求要有）\r\n\r\n女方：月入 4000 ，无社保（私立教师，大老板人大